===Etymology===
This character was invented c.&thinsp;1910, following the earlier [[皮酒]] as a transliteration of English ''beer'' and German ''Bier''.[http://www.360doc.com/content/10/0414/15/805886_23026069.shtml] It is composed of a semantic [[口]] (mouth, food, beverage) + phonetic [[卑]].

